## Groups

### Rename a group

```ts
const updatedChat = await im.groups.setDisplayName(chatGuid, "New Group Name");
```

### Manage participants

```ts
const updatedChat2 = await im.groups.addParticipants(chatGuid, ["newperson@icloud.com"]);
const updatedChat3 = await im.groups.removeParticipants(chatGuid, ["oldperson@icloud.com"]);
```

### Group icons

```ts
const icon = await im.groups.getIcon(chatGuid);

await im.groups.setIcon(chatGuid, imageBytes);

await im.groups.removeIcon(chatGuid);
```

### Leave a group

```ts
await im.groups.leave(chatGuid);
```

### Group events

Group changes are emitted as a single `group.changed` event with a discriminated `change` field:

```ts
for await (const event of im.groups.subscribeEvents()) {
  switch (event.change.type) {
    case "displayNameChanged":
      console.log("New name:", event.change.displayName);
      break;
    case "participantAdded":
      console.log("Added:", event.change.participant.address);
      break;
    case "participantRemoved":
      console.log("Removed:", event.change.participant.address);
      break;
    case "iconChanged":
    case "iconRemoved":
      break;
  }
}
```

